1
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,400
What's this?

2
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:58,960
Coroner Li,

3
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,120
any findings?

4
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:04,400
The victim's eyes are missing,

5
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,540
and the eye sockets are a bloody mess.

6
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:09,680
They were likely gouged out with a sharp weapon.

7
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:11,480
The method was extremely cruel.

8
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:14,960
The fingernails were forcibly removed.

9
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:17,480
The body is covered with knife wounds

10
00:02:17,480 --> 00:02:19,800
of varying lengths and widths.

11
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:22,240
They likely weren't inflicted all at once.

12
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,760
The dagger was thrust straight into the heart.

13
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:26,200
Judging from the depth,

14
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,920
this should be the fatal wound.

15
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:28,800
Also,

16
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:32,720
this dagger matches the one in Madam Cao's chest.

17
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:35,640
Go quickly and check if the murder weapon is still in Madam Cao's chest.

18
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,200
Hurry up. Okay.

19
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:38,560
Hurry. Let's go. Okay.

20
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,160
The dagger is missing!

21
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,600
Go report it!

22
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,480
Let's go. Okay.

23
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:11,120
It's gone. It's gone.

24
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:14,240
The dagger in Mrs. Cao's chest is gone.

25
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:17,640
This dagger belonged to my late father.

26
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:19,440
Six jewels are inlaid on its blade.

27
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:20,680
It is named Liuxing.

28
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:23,380
It is the only one of its kind in the world.

29
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:27,640
Just now, I asked you two

30
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:30,120
to carry Mrs. Cao's body into the room.

31
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:32,000
Was the dagger still there at that time?

32
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,840
Yes, it was.

33
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,640
Which means...

34
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:43,160
Master Yuan was murdered after we settled Mrs. Cao's body.

35
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:45,720
Compiler Dong.

36
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:48,880
Look at how Master Yuan died.

37
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:53,120
Doesn't it look like...

38
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:56,360
Doesn't it look like...

39
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:01,840
The deaths of Master Yuan and Mrs. Cao

40
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:06,880
are exactly the same as what Young Master Cao wrote in his book.

41
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:09,520
At first, I thought it was a coincidence.

42
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,400
But now...

43
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,520
This...

44
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:16,640
This was deliberately done by the suspect!

45
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,839
In that case,

46
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,440
you are the murderer.

47
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,720
I am not.

48
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:26,530
Although his death matches the one in my book,

49
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,560
it really has nothing to do with me.

50
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,920
This is really bizarre.

51
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:30,520
Don't be afraid.

52
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:32,640
It really wasn't me. Don't be afraid. Don't be afraid.

53
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:35,600
Beside Mrs. Cao's body is the first volume.

54
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:39,560
Beside Master Yuan is the second volume.

55
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:41,320
It seems the murderer

56
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:45,050
wants to guide us to finish reading "The Scheme of Fake Pregnancy".

57
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:53,920
Push.

58
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,840
Push hard.

59
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,159
Push, push.

60
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:58,400
The head is out.

61
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,240
Hold on. The baby is coming.

62
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:10,200
The baby is here.

63
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,370
The baby is born.

64
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:17,280
It's a boy.

65
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,840
Thank goodness.

66
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:21,160
After two girls in a row,

67
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,640
I was getting worried.

68
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:27,880
Look how much he looks like you.

69
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,560
You may all leave.

70
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,760
Yes.

71
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,520
Look at our baby.

72
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:54,800
I want to see the baby.

73
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,400
Alright, take a look.

74
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,960
Oh, wow!

75
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:13,280
So chubby and fair!

76
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,400
Here.

77
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,920
Look, the baby.

78
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,200
My baby.

79
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:21,080
Come look at your baby.

80
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:22,160
The baby.

81
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:23,640
Let me see.

82
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:24,960
Show me.

83
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:17,120
Eunuch, Consort Zhao gave birth to a baby boy.

84
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:19,040
It's a baby boy.

85
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:22,880
I will go report to the Emperor right now.

86
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:33,680
The other pregnant women in Consort Zhao's residence were all silenced

87
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,320
and buried in the back mountain.

88
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,120
From then on,

89
00:07:36,159 --> 00:07:39,800
the palace claimed these pregnant women had never been here.

90
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:45,640
Perhaps due to the heavy negative energy,

91
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:48,520
these dead babies turned into vengeful spirits.

92
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:52,480
Various supernatural events began to happen in the whole residence.

93
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:57,400
Why is there still crying?

94
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:58,240
That shouldn't be.

95
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,360
Right.

96
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,760
Why is this chair moving?

97
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,960
Go take a look.

98
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,200
Right after that,

99
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:22,200
a murder occurred in the palace.

100
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:24,760
The first was Consort Zhao's mother.

101
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:27,560
The second was Imperial Physician Sun.

102
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,920
And their state of death

103
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:33,280
was exactly the same as the two murders at the villa.

104
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:41,799
It seems the suspect has read this book thoroughly,

105
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:44,080
knows its contents inside out,

106
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:47,800
and is copying its murder methods.

107
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:51,280
How many copies of this book were printed?

108
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:53,400
Who has read it?

109
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,720
That would be a lot.

110
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,720
For the first trial printing and publication,

111
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,850
there were no less than 100 reviewers.

112
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:02,080
This gathering

113
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,760
was also meant as an opportunity

114
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:06,680
to collect words of praise from you gentlemen

115
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:09,920
for future book promotions.

116
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:13,800
If the suspect is copying the book's methods,

117
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:15,120
who is the real killer?

118
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,560
And what is the ending?

119
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:20,560
The ending is that everyone is killed by a ghost one by one.

120
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:22,560
The killer is among them

121
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,900
but hasn't been found.

122
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:26,560
Why wasn't the real killer caught?

123
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:30,040
I originally wanted to leave a hook for the sequel.

124
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,920
I haven't decided who the killer is yet.

125
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:33,080
I just thought

126
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:35,360
people might like reading it this way.

127
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:37,280
Isn't this kid harming others and himself?

128
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,640
Still writing a sequel?

129
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:40,360
What you should worry about most is

130
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,760
who will be the killer's next target.

131
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:46,400
No matter what the suspect's motive is,

132
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:49,040
or why they are copying the book,

133
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:51,480
these are not our concerns.

134
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:54,720
We should leave this place right now.

135
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,800
Right.

136
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:57,400
I shouldn't have come. Let's go, hurry up.

137
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:58,960
Stop! Leave immediately!

138
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,480
No one can leave.

139
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,400
Why?

140
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:04,200
The suspect is hiding among us right now.

141
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,600
If everyone just leaves,

142
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,760
he will take the chance to escape.

143
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:08,280
We absolutely cannot do that.

144
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,800
You mean we should be trapped here? But soon,

145
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:12,200
we'll be sitting ducks. We're going to die here.

146
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,240
We will find out the truth.

147
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:15,680
We can't just wait here. Won't we all die here?

148
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:17,210
We are from the government.

149
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,880
It's getting late.

150
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:22,560
Why don't you all head back to the government office with me.

151
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:24,200
We'll investigate one by one,

152
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,480
and question everyone,

153
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,880
until we find the real culprit.

154
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:28,320
This works.

155
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:29,720
It's feasible.

156
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:30,560
Young Master.

157
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,480
Slow down.

158
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,920
This way, this way.

159
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:48,680
Where is the boat?

160
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,120
Why is it gone?

161
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,360
How could the boats be gone? They were right here during the day.

162
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,320
Yeah.

163
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,200
Is there any other way back?

164
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,960
This is the only waterway from the villa to the outside.

165
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:01,220
Without boats, there is no other way out.

166
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:03,680
The ropes. Someone cut them on purpose.

167
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:05,880
The suspect let the boats loose on purpose.

168
00:11:05,880 --> 00:11:07,800
It seems they want to trap us here.

169
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:12,800
The killing hasn't stopped.

170
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,900
It must have been carefully planned.

171
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:18,640
The killer must know the villa like the back of their hand.

172
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:19,840
Right?

173
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,200
I want to go back.

174
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,520
I want to go back.

175
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,280
Are there really no other boats?

176
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:25,280
Calm down, young master.

177
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:26,560
Where is the boat, young master?

178
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:29,440
Every day at Mao hour, a boat comes to deliver fresh vegetables.

179
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,400
At other times,

180
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:33,120
we rely on the four boats docked at the pier to ferry people.

181
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,480
What time is it now?

182
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:35,680
What time is it now?

183
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,800
What time is it now, young master?

184
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,520
It should be Xu hour.

185
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,720
Since we can't leave,

186
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:46,040
the safest thing to do is to return to the villa.

187
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:47,720
Everyone gather in the hall.

188
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,560
No one should go anywhere alone.

189
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:52,890
That way, the killer won't have a chance to strike again.

190
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,520
We are...

191
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:57,120
missing someone.

192
00:11:57,160 --> 00:11:58,560
Someone is missing!

193
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:03,080
Where is the steward?

194
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,120
Where did the steward go?

195
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,680
I haven't seen him for a while.

196
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:07,600
Yeah, where did he go?

197
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:13,880
It seems the servant who came with me is also gone.

198
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:16,290
Why didn't he stay with you?

199
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:19,480
Why didn't you mention your servant earlier?

200
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,720
Wasn't he with you?

201
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:22,080
Seeing him so panicked,

202
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,240
there must be something suspicious.

203
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:25,680
- Why didn't you mention your servant earlier?
- I didn't know either!

204
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:27,000
Stop arguing.

205
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:28,160
Enough!

206
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,400
Listen to me.

207
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,480
Our top priority now

208
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:37,340
is to find the killer and the two missing people.

209
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:40,640
And I suspect the killer is among us.

210
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:45,360
Waiting here until Mao hour is not an option.

211
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,720
It's so dark outside.

212
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,720
The suspect might strike again.

213
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:50,640
Right now, the only safe way

214
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:52,280
is for us to stick together,

215
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:53,360
go back the way we came,

216
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:55,720
and find the two missing people first.

217
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,280
You lead the way.

218
00:12:58,440 --> 00:13:00,160
Young master, stay close to me.

219
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:01,400
Stay close to me.

220
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,740
Stay close. Go, go, go.

221
00:13:02,760 --> 00:13:03,640
Hurry up.

222
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:04,760
Walk faster.

223
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,800
Come, this way.

224
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:12,600
Keep up.

225
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:15,200
Manager Zhang, hurry up.

226
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,520
Come, keep up.

227
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:18,160
Achi.

228
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:22,440
Manager.

229
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,920
Manager Zhang. Manager Zhang.

230
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:28,200
Manager Zhang.

231
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:29,920
Chi.

232
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:31,480
Chi.

233
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:34,280
Chi.

234
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,480
Wake up.

235
00:13:35,680 --> 00:13:36,520
Chi.

236
00:13:36,560 --> 00:13:37,640
Wake up.

237
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,320
Are you okay?

238
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,600
Come help him up.

239
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:42,400
Careful.

240
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,920
Another one dead.

241
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:47,960
Nobody move.

242
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:55,840
The killer is so brutal.

243
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:02,090
Go check on that person.

244
00:14:13,880 --> 00:14:15,840
The victim's head was severed.

245
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:22,280
The neck incision is clean.

246
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:26,650
It should be caused by being quickly cut off with a sharp weapon.

247
00:14:27,520 --> 00:14:30,980
The dagger in the chest is exactly the same as the previous one.

248
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:34,600
According to the wound and surrounding signs,

249
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:37,880
he must have been stabbed directly in the chest with a dagger,

250
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:40,320
injuring his vital organs and causing his death,

251
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:42,050
before having his head cut off.

252
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:48,000
According to the residual temperature of the hand,

253
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,080
the time of death was not long ago.

254
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:54,280
Why did you faint here?

255
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,520
Did you see anything?

256
00:14:59,040 --> 00:15:01,280
I also heard a noise here when I was going down the mountain,

257
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:02,520
so I rushed over.

258
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,960
But as soon as I came,

259
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:05,880
I was knocked out.

260
00:15:05,920 --> 00:15:07,160
Who knocked you out?

261
00:15:08,560 --> 00:15:10,000
I didn't see clearly.

262
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:12,880
A Chi, think carefully.

263
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:15,810
Why did so many people die tonight?

264
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:18,320
And who killed the steward?

265
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:20,160
Everyone was in a hurry to go down the mountain and escape for their lives.

266
00:15:20,160 --> 00:15:22,120
Who would notice him?

267
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:25,600
This is to kill us all.

268
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:26,880
No.

269
00:15:26,920 --> 00:15:28,720
I'm leaving. I'm leaving.

270
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:30,840
Even without a boat, I'll swim back.

271
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:31,560
No one can leave.

272
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:33,120
If you leave now,

273
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:34,800
the next one to die

274
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:36,960
might be you.

275
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:39,640
Right, you can't leave.

276
00:15:39,760 --> 00:15:41,360
In case you are the murderer,

277
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:43,760
wouldn't you escape just like that?

278
00:15:44,920 --> 00:15:46,280
What do you mean?

279
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:48,440
I've been walking with you all the way.

280
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,880
We haven't left each other for a step.

281
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:51,560
How could I kill someone?

282
00:15:51,680 --> 00:15:53,880
Right? You all saw me.

283
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,280
Sir.

284
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,680
Just now when we were walking together,

285
00:16:00,680 --> 00:16:04,880
I saw you slip back into your room alone.

286
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,520
What were you doing?

287
00:16:06,920 --> 00:16:08,200
Say something.

288
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:10,320
Tell us.

289
00:16:11,120 --> 00:16:13,560
I went to get my luggage.

290
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:15,600
Get your luggage? Luggage?

291
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:17,880
You are empty-handed.

292
00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:19,560
You are clearly lying.

293
00:16:19,920 --> 00:16:22,680
Yeah, where is your luggage?

294
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:31,120
Madam Jiang gave this to me.

295
00:16:31,520 --> 00:16:32,920
Nonsense.

296
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:36,960
You're just a scholar. Why would she give you so many gold bars?

297
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:43,040
Could they be from Master Yuan?

298
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:45,200
That's right. You killed Master Yuan.

299
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:47,240
And you took his gold bars.

300
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:48,040
It was you!

301
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:50,320
I didn't kill Master Yuan.

302
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:51,160
It was you.

303
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:53,880
He put these gold bars in the room himself.

304
00:16:55,280 --> 00:16:56,800
I saw Master Yuan with my own eyes,

305
00:16:56,800 --> 00:16:59,400
sneaking the gold bars under his pillow.

306
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,640
When I was going down the mountain,

307
00:17:03,640 --> 00:17:06,200
I remembered the gold bars were still in the room,

308
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:08,319
so I went back to the room and took them.

309
00:17:08,319 --> 00:17:10,400
But as for where Master Yuan got them,

310
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:11,800
I have no idea.

311
00:17:12,520 --> 00:17:14,319
If what you say is true,

312
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:15,520
those gold bars

313
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:22,970
must have been given to him by his mother to buy books.

314
00:17:24,560 --> 00:17:26,880
My mother gave him two gold bars.

315
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,860
When the new book went on sale,

316
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:31,000
she wanted him to secretly buy it in batches

317
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:33,930
to create the illusion that my book is a best-seller,

318
00:17:34,040 --> 00:17:36,300
thus attracting everyone's attention.

319
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:39,280
Speaking of suspicion,

320
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,000
I think you're a suspect too.

321
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:47,320
Owner Yuan originally wanted to promote your new work, right?

322
00:17:47,360 --> 00:17:50,760
But Mr. Cao's new book was finished first,

323
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:53,120
so yours was put on hold.

324
00:17:53,360 --> 00:17:56,720
I think you held a grudge against the Cao family

325
00:17:56,760 --> 00:17:58,880
and decided to kill him, didn't you?

326
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:01,600
I held a grudge?

327
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:04,680
If I really held a grudge,

328
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:07,480
the first person I would kill is Cao Wen.

329
00:18:08,080 --> 00:18:11,640
It has nothing to do with Owner Yuan and Manager Zhang.

330
00:18:14,280 --> 00:18:16,560
And Scholar Jiang,

331
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:19,130
you're having an affair with Mrs. Cao.

332
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:21,920
No matter how dissatisfied I am,

333
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:24,360
I'd still have to show you some respect.

334
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:26,480
Nonsense!

335
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:27,920
Wait.

336
00:18:31,560 --> 00:18:33,400
When I came to the villa today,

337
00:18:33,440 --> 00:18:37,040
I immediately asked a servant to take me to Mrs. Cao.

338
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:40,240
I wanted to present the gifts I brought to her.

339
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:43,520
Madam,

340
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:46,720
here are some selected gifts for you.

341
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:48,840
It's enough that you came.

342
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:50,880
There's no need for gifts.

343
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:54,480
I accidentally noticed

344
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:57,840
a cabinet door by her bed wasn't closed properly.

345
00:18:58,200 --> 00:19:01,320
There was a piece of a sleeve in that gap.

346
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:03,610
I didn't pay much attention to it then.

347
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,560
But thinking about it now...

348
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:09,920
Scholar Jiang,

349
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:13,960
Your sleeve and the one caught in the door

350
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:15,840
look quite similar.

351
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:20,240
Could the person in the wardrobe be you?

352
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:23,240
I haven't been to the east wing today.

353
00:19:24,320 --> 00:19:25,320
Scholar Jiang,

354
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:28,080
I escorted you there this afternoon.

355
00:19:28,760 --> 00:19:31,800
So you do have an affair with Madam.

356
00:19:34,080 --> 00:19:36,880
I have no involvement with Madam Cao.

357
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:39,200
I was just discussing Cao Wen's work with her.

358
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:41,400
What does this have to do with the case?

359
00:19:42,040 --> 00:19:44,920
Most murders are committed by acquaintances.

360
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,240
Either for money,

361
00:19:46,280 --> 00:19:47,960
or for love and revenge.

362
00:19:48,120 --> 00:19:50,180
All kinds of personal entanglements

363
00:19:50,200 --> 00:19:51,920
could hide trouble.

364
00:19:52,080 --> 00:19:54,800
Our investigation is like unspooling silk.

365
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:58,000
We need to clarify everyone's relationship with the deceased.

366
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:59,720
That makes sense. It does.

367
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:01,080
In the current situation,

368
00:20:01,080 --> 00:20:02,200
with so many people talking,

369
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:03,860
it's hard to avoid confusion.

370
00:20:04,040 --> 00:20:05,120
To seek the truth,

371
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:08,280
everyone, please return to your rooms for now.

372
00:20:08,520 --> 00:20:09,760
Stay separated,

373
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:11,040
and don't collude.

374
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:13,920
That makes sense.

375
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:15,320
Chief Su,

376
00:20:16,120 --> 00:20:17,720
you must personally search

377
00:20:17,760 --> 00:20:20,000
every item in everyone's room

378
00:20:20,040 --> 00:20:21,440
to find clues

379
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:23,010
and catch the real culprit.

380
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:27,840
Just as you expected,

381
00:20:27,960 --> 00:20:30,220
the dagger on Master Yuan's body is gone.

382
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:33,040
The suspect first killed Madam Cao with a dagger,

383
00:20:33,040 --> 00:20:35,080
then pulled it out to kill Master Yuan,

384
00:20:35,080 --> 00:20:37,940
and finally pulled it out again to kill the manager.

385
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,480
Even if committing the murders,

386
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:41,640
why use the same dagger?

387
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:46,160
Could this dagger have some special meaning?

388
00:20:48,320 --> 00:20:51,520
The first body was found in the backyard,

389
00:20:51,840 --> 00:20:54,640
with the first volume of "The Plot of False Pregnancy" next to it.

390
00:20:54,640 --> 00:20:57,480
The second body was found in the granary,

391
00:20:58,040 --> 00:21:01,700
with the second volume of "The Plot of False Pregnancy" next to it.

392
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:04,200
The third body was found in the inner hall,

393
00:21:04,360 --> 00:21:07,200
with the third volume of "The Plot of False Pregnancy" next to it.

394
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:08,480
Based on this,

395
00:21:08,520 --> 00:21:11,560
one would naturally think the order of death is Madam Cao,

396
00:21:11,560 --> 00:21:13,760
Master Yuan, and the manager.

397
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:18,240
But what if there is more than one identical dagger?

398
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:20,160
At Madam Cao's crime scene,

399
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:21,740
we didn't see Master Yuan,

400
00:21:21,840 --> 00:21:25,440
which means Master Yuan died before Madam Cao.

401
00:21:25,520 --> 00:21:28,400
The suspect only needed to prepare two identical daggers

402
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:31,400
to create confusion about the victims' times of death.

403
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:33,730
He first helped Master Yuan to the granary

404
00:21:33,760 --> 00:21:35,720
and then killed him.

405
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:37,520
He left the murder weapon

406
00:21:37,640 --> 00:21:40,200
and placed the second volume of the book on the table.

407
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:42,520
Right after, he went to the backyard.

408
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:45,680
Then he killed Madam Cao.

409
00:21:46,120 --> 00:21:48,160
He stabbed her with another identical dagger

410
00:21:48,160 --> 00:21:49,960
and left the first volume of the book.

411
00:21:49,960 --> 00:21:50,640
Next,

412
00:21:50,680 --> 00:21:54,080
he found a way to let someone discover Madam Cao's body first.

413
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:57,440
While transporting Madam Cao's body,

414
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:59,240
he took the dagger away.

415
00:21:59,440 --> 00:22:01,360
When we found Master Yuan's body

416
00:22:01,440 --> 00:22:03,040
and caused a commotion,

417
00:22:03,240 --> 00:22:05,440
the killer took advantage of everyone fleeing the manor.

418
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:08,120
At this time, he pulled the manager aside and said

419
00:22:08,120 --> 00:22:09,520
he saw the real culprit.

420
00:22:09,600 --> 00:22:11,000
The manager believed him

421
00:22:11,040 --> 00:22:13,880
and thus became the third victim.

422
00:22:14,240 --> 00:22:16,560
He took the dagger from Madam Cao's body

423
00:22:16,840 --> 00:22:18,600
and stabbed it into the manager.

424
00:22:18,600 --> 00:22:21,360
Then he took the dagger from Master Yuan's body.

425
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:23,440
Next, he quickly went down the mountain

426
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:25,700
and followed everyone back to the manor.

427
00:22:25,920 --> 00:22:28,760
The person who could cut the boat rope in advance, hint Gu Yitong to go to the backyard,

428
00:22:28,760 --> 00:22:31,080
take the dagger while transporting Madam Cao's body,

429
00:22:31,080 --> 00:22:32,640
kill the manager,

430
00:22:33,280 --> 00:22:34,840
and knock out the servant Achi before

431
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:36,680
rushing to the ferry,

432
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:41,360
could only be another servant in the residence.

433
00:22:43,680 --> 00:22:44,720
Based on deduction,

434
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:46,440
"The Plot of False Pregnancy" has four volumes.

435
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:49,240
He still hides the dagger that killed Master Yuan,

436
00:22:49,240 --> 00:22:50,880
preparing to strike again.

437
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:53,480
So, you arranged for everyone to return to their rooms first

438
00:22:53,480 --> 00:22:55,810
and let Chief Su check the rooms one by one.

439
00:22:57,320 --> 00:22:58,800
The current suspect

440
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:02,330
will definitely take the risk to throw this dagger away.

441
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:13,160
Liu Renjiu.

442
00:23:20,280 --> 00:23:21,880
You are indeed the murderer.

443
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:24,200
It wasn't me. I was framed.

444
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:25,480
After I went back to my room,

445
00:23:25,480 --> 00:23:27,800
I found a bloody dagger under my pillow.

446
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:31,160
This... this isn't mine.

447
00:23:31,520 --> 00:23:33,000
Afraid I couldn't explain it,

448
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:34,680
I decided to throw it into the lake.

449
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:36,480
Do you think I'd believe you?

450
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,760
It really wasn't me.

451
00:23:40,800 --> 00:23:42,200
The Cao family has treated me well.

452
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:43,480
Why would I have a reason to kill anyone?

453
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:44,880
It really wasn't me.

454
00:23:45,360 --> 00:23:46,840
Brother Jueming, Miss.

455
00:23:47,560 --> 00:23:48,440
What's wrong?

456
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:50,080
Another body has been found.

457
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:06,760
Stand up straight.

458
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:19,560
You killed him too.

459
00:24:19,600 --> 00:24:21,200
Tell me, did you kill him?

460
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:22,160
It wasn't me.

461
00:24:22,680 --> 00:24:24,080
He lives in the west wing.

462
00:24:24,080 --> 00:24:25,520
I live in the utility room.

463
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:28,680
To go to his room, I'd definitely have to pass through the inner hall.

464
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:31,520
Besides, how could I kill him in such a short time

465
00:24:31,560 --> 00:24:35,490
and then return to the pond by the utility room to throw away the dagger?

466
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:38,920
Su Lang.

467
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:41,080
How did you find the body?

468
00:24:41,840 --> 00:24:44,000
I waited until everyone went back to their rooms,

469
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:46,840
then searched them from east to west.

470
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:49,880
I found nothing suspicious in the rooms I checked.

471
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:51,400
Boss Gu.

472
00:24:53,680 --> 00:24:55,200
When I got to Boss Gu's room,

473
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,680
I knocked softly but got no answer.

474
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:57,840
So I pushed the door open

475
00:24:57,840 --> 00:24:59,440
and found him dead inside.

476
00:25:02,760 --> 00:25:04,220
Take good care of Jinglan.

477
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:05,480
Okay.

478
00:25:07,280 --> 00:25:08,280
Miss Li,

479
00:25:08,320 --> 00:25:09,800
you must stand up for me.

480
00:25:09,840 --> 00:25:11,240
Even if you gave me ten times the courage,

481
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:13,000
I wouldn't dare kill so many people.

482
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:15,240
I swear it really wasn't me.

483
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:22,720
The dagger is indeed gone.

484
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:25,800
I went straight from the inner hall to the pond.

485
00:25:25,840 --> 00:25:29,040
When I left, the butler had a dagger on him.

486
00:25:29,080 --> 00:25:30,760
Under these circumstances,

487
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:34,440
even if Liu Renjiu had the chance to kill Boss Gu,

488
00:25:35,240 --> 00:25:39,440
he wouldn't have had time to take the dagger from the butler.

489
00:25:41,840 --> 00:25:44,120
Was my deduction really wrong?

490
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:47,480
Liu Renjiu isn't the real killer.

491
00:25:47,520 --> 00:25:49,840
He was framed.

492
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:52,920
But if that's really the case,

493
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:54,920
I dismissed everyone

494
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:57,080
and asked them to return to their rooms.

495
00:25:57,080 --> 00:26:00,480
This instead gave the killer an opportunity to strike again.

496
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:12,280
There are still two volumes of the book unread.

497
00:26:12,280 --> 00:26:14,240
The answer might be in them.

498
00:26:17,640 --> 00:26:20,760
Strange supernatural events kept happening in the palace.

499
00:26:20,760 --> 00:26:23,000
And then a third victim appeared.

500
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,040
Xiao Shunzi.

501
00:26:26,400 --> 00:26:29,840
Xiao Shunzi died tragically in the embroidery room, beheaded.

502
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:32,200
A dagger was also stuck in his chest.

503
00:26:32,520 --> 00:26:34,080
Consort Zhao felt guilty.

504
00:26:34,120 --> 00:26:35,880
She believed her servants' words,

505
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:37,940
and invited someone to catch ghosts.

506
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:40,530
A Taoist master came to the palace,

507
00:26:40,560 --> 00:26:42,840
along with a shaman and a retainer.

508
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:47,120
The Taoist master performed rituals and gave everyone amulets for safety.

509
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:48,720
The shaman possessed the dead body

510
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:50,960
and spoke the deceased's grievances.

511
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:52,860
To determine who the murderer is.

512
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:57,480
But both methods seemed utterly absurd to the retainer.

513
00:26:57,680 --> 00:27:00,740
He believed it must be a living person causing trouble.

514
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:03,320
After some searching,

515
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:06,640
the retainer found the pregnant woman's corpse buried in the back mountain,

516
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:10,100
thus discovering the truth about Consort Zhao having a child.

517
00:27:10,120 --> 00:27:14,960
Consort Zhao's mother, Imperial Physician Sun, and Xiaoshunzi died one after another.

518
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:18,000
This indicated that the suspect was highly likely seeking revenge.

519
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:21,040
The retainer carefully checked all personnel movements in the residence,

520
00:27:21,040 --> 00:27:23,640
and found that a batch of eunuchs was recently recruited.

521
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:26,200
The suspect was very likely among them.

522
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:29,600
The suspect's wife was the pregnant woman,

523
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:31,760
who was recruited into the palace for embroidery work.

524
00:27:31,760 --> 00:27:33,560
and never returned home.

525
00:27:33,600 --> 00:27:35,320
To find out the truth,

526
00:27:35,360 --> 00:27:37,690
he entered the palace and became a eunuch.

527
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:40,040
Just as there was a new clue in the case,

528
00:27:40,040 --> 00:27:43,320
a shrill scream echoed through the palace.

529
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:45,360
Consort Zhao is dead.

530
00:27:51,800 --> 00:27:54,600
The retainer realized he was still a step too late.

531
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:55,960
The fake pregnancy bundle

532
00:27:55,960 --> 00:27:58,520
was put back onto Consort Zhao's abdomen.

533
00:27:59,320 --> 00:28:00,400
Judging from this,

534
00:28:00,520 --> 00:28:04,180
the child taken by Consort Zhao was the suspect's flesh and blood.

535
00:28:04,480 --> 00:28:06,200
After taking revenge on Consort Zhao,

536
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:08,400
he would definitely take the child away.

537
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:10,400
The retainer rushed to the royal nursery

538
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:12,330
and found the baby was still there.

539
00:28:12,600 --> 00:28:15,160
However, as he turned around,

540
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:18,520
a sharp blade pierced his chest.

541
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:30,080
A story of a Virtuous Consort faking a pregnancy in the palace.

542
00:28:30,080 --> 00:28:32,680
Why imitate this story to commit murder?

